{"tid":1142653,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"tony 死咗之後好唔開心...好想再睇翻佢","createTime":"2019-05-07T08:14:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-07T09:35:03.000Z","uid":112303,"like":4,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"89c2fc6c34e5e4b5f2e089b0c584230a4458742a","tid":1142653,"uid":112303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T08:14:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好想再睇佢教波<br />\nTony Sparano passed away unexpectedly on Sunday.  USATSI<br />\nVikings offensive line coach Tony Sparano died of natural causes brought on by arteriosclerotic heart disease, the Hennepin County Medical Examiner announced on Monday.  <br />\nThe 56-year-old passed away unexpectedly on Sunday morning, just two days before Vikings rookies were set to report to training camp. According to <a href=\"http://ESPN.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FESPN.com&d=BbGirfR5U81eMP64OYU5HJhbjDs%2B%2F0Yai8vOOt2IPjE%3D&h=af356947\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">ESPN.com</a>, an unconscious Sparano was discovered by his wife at their home in Eden Prairie on Sunday as the family was getting prepared to leave for church. Sparano's official time of death was 8:54 a.m.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.cbssports.com/nfl/news/tony-sparanos-cause-of-death-released-by-medical-examiner-in-minnesota/amp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Fwww.cbssports.com%2Fnfl%2Fnews%2Ftony-sparanos-cause-of-death-released-by-medical-examiner-in-minnesota%2Famp%2F&d=BbGirfR5U81eMP64OYU5HJhbjDs%2B%2F0Yai8vOOt2IPjE%3D&h=798bc303\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.cbssports.com/nfl/news/tony-sparanos-cause-of-death-released-by-medical-examiner-in-minnesota/amp/</a>"},{"pid":"de83b125f8d3ea22a190492fbbd0cd562f051ae4","tid":1142653,"uid":112303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T08:16:49.000Z","msg":"好懷念 有無人睇